<p><iframe src="https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--code/info%3Astyle/5" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="" width="" class="close-credits" style="height:2em;margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;background: transparent;"></iframe></p>
<p><strong>Numbers <span style="text-decoration: line-through;">don't</span> lie</strong><br />
<strong>Author:</strong> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/citytoast" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1372124); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1372124&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609721469" alt="CityToast" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1372124)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/citytoast" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1372124); return false;">CityToast</a></span></p>
<p>I've finally decided to make a leap into the <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/antimemetics-division-hub">Antimemetics Division</a>. Since I first read <em><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/we-need-to-talk-about-fifty-five">We Need To Talk About Fifty-Five</a></em> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/qntm" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(571081); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=571081&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609721469" alt="qntm" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=571081)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/qntm" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(571081); return false;">qntm</a></span> back in 2015 I have loved Wheeler and have been determined that, if I ever start writing SCPs again, I'd write an Antimemetic Division story. Well, here I am and here it is.</p>
<p>Thank you also to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/hammermaiden" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1552358); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1552358&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609721469" alt="HammerMaiden" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1552358)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/hammermaiden" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1552358); return false;">HammerMaiden</a></span> for writing such a cool SCP back in '17.</p>
<p><em>Trivia</em>: An exchange I cut out of this story, because it didn't fit the mood, was Elanor calling the memetic people <em>meeple</em>.</p>
<p>Also: I understand that under the correct circumstances you could get 6 billion people with SCP-2000. It would just involve a lot of forced pairings, underage pregnancies, and other things which I didn't want to include in this tale. So I took some liberties.</p>
